{"word":"τριέτης","slug":"τριέτης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>τριέτης</b></el> <el>(τρι-έτης, ου,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἔτος'><el>ἔτος</el></a>\n<p/><i>of</i> or <i>for three years</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b>: netut. <el>τριέτες</el> as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <i>for three years</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/>"}]}